                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920704-6-off29 t17920704-6-cd30"></join>, a watch, inside base metal, outside tortoiseshell case, value 50 s. a steel chain, value 2 s. two stone seals, set in base metal, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17920704-6-victim139" type="victimName">
